high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then turn left again and walk towards the door, turn right and walk up to the dresser.
Pick up the leftmost disc off of the dresser.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the mirror, turn right again to face the end of the dresser.
Turn on the light of the small lamp on the end of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Examine a disc in the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the left side of the dresser.
Pick up the leftmost CD on the dresser.
Walk left to the mirror, then turn and face the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a CD by the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the center of the bed, then turn right and move to the dresser against the wall.
Pick up the CD between the two smartphones from the top of the dresser.
Turn left, move to the mirror on the wall to the left of the dresser, then turn right and face the left side of the dresser.
Turn on the lamp on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Examine a CD using the light from a lamp.
